{
  "texts": [
    "Only MAGIC has reported performance on this platform with communication, and more investigations on this environment are needed.",
    "Compared to the above approaches in Comm-MADRL, ATOC [38] has been examined using a significantly larger number of learning agents in the predator-prey domain.",
    "Predator-prey is a grid world game with a long history in MARL.",
    "It has been developed with several versions [7,99,100], while still viewed as a standard test environment due to its flexibility and customizability.",
    "ATOC reports performance on this platform with continuous state and action spaces."
  ]
}